title: MSN.Live.Messenger.8.5.1302.1018 (works without updating)
description:
For those who dislike the latest version of MSN Messenger Live 9.0+ this was the only version that worked for -me- where it didn't FORCE you to update when you try to sign-in. Hope it's the same for you guys (if that's what you're looking for that is) DL&Seed :)

Make sure you uninstall your current version of MSN first, restart, and install this one. It should install into directory by default C:_Program Files_Windows Live_Messenger 

The underscores are to represent backslashes because for some reason they won't show in TPB.
